@startuml AD_LT_01_Upload_Test_Report

title AD_LT_01 — Upload Test Report

|Lab Technician|
|System|

|Lab Technician|

note
  Prerequisites:
  - AD_LT_00 User Authenticated
  - Doctor order exists in system
end note

start

:Open test queue;
:Select test order by urgency / order ID;

|System|

:Display order details\n(patient, test type, doctor, notes);
:Validate result entry;

|Lab Technician|

:Enter result values manually\nor attach file (PDF/CSV/image ≤25 MB);

|System|

if (File attached?) then (yes)
  if (File valid?\nformat + size ≤25 MB) then (no)
    :Show inline error;
    |Lab Technician|
    :Correct file and re-attach;
    |System|
  endif
endif

:Compare values against\nclinical reference ranges;

if (Abnormal result?) then (yes)
  :Flag result with\ncolour-coded indicator;
  :Send urgent alert\nto requesting doctor;
else (no)
endif

:Save report linked to\npatient record + doctor order;
:Record timestamp\n+ technician ID;
:Notify requesting doctor\n(report ready);

|Lab Technician|

:View upload confirmation\n+ audit log entry;

stop

@enduml
